----------Layer thickness iteration mode----------
-----(Only for special case of 2 layers and substrate infinite and 
	no independent invisibles in substrate)-----
-1	(-1 if inactive, otherwise: 1=upper layer iterated,
	2=substrate iterated.)
----------Define invisible elements----------
2	(Integer number of invisible elements or compounds; otherwise -1 if no
	invisibles or if it is not a matrix element solution.)
	(If no invisibles, a single -1 entry. Otherwise 1 line for each invisible:
