	with (Z comma atomic fraction) for each atom in the compound): 2nd item is 
	the layer # or NL if not layered: 3rd is valence of invisible: 4th is
	dependent/independent=1/-1: 5th is the altered list of complexes, or -1 
	if no alterations/removals made.)
6 NL 4 1 -1
